snippet.title: Overlook Trail - Launch trailer
snippet.description:
Play it now on Steam: https://s.team/a/817800 

Embark on Overlook Trail, a mixtape of arcade gameplay, 3D platforming, and peculiar puzzles. Navigate through surreal landscapes with ever-changing challenges.

Overlook Trail is available for Windows PC, Mac, Linux and Steam Deck.

Overlook Trail features music by:
Caroline Karpinska
Douglas Holmquist
Niklas Ström
Pelle Hillström

Cover/intro art by: Kazu Saitou
